Kyocera falls on decline in orders for May . Kyocera Corp ' s shares fell in the Friday session on profit - taking , sparked by news of a decline in the firm ' s orders for May , brokers said . A spokeswoman told Reuters that orders had fallen 15 percent on a year - on - year basis in May . As of 0518 GMT , the shares of the ceramic package maker were down 260 yen at 8 , 770 . 
